e 8-hour TWAP of the premium between perpetual and spot prices. The funding payment occurs at the top of each hour between long and short position holders. dYdX's Cosmos appchain ensures fast settlement of funding payments with no gas fees for users. The exchange uses a 0.02% maker and 0.05% taker fee structure that impacts net arbitrage profitability calculations."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
